P_HTM[4605]="*10. Tatiyaanattasuttaṃ**Not*";
P_HTM[4606]="*Sāvatthinidānaṃ.**At Sāvatthī.*";
P_HTM[4607]="*“Yo, bhikkhave, anattā; tatra vo chandarāgo pahātabbo.**“Mendicants, you should give up desire and greed for what is not-self. …”*";
P_HTM[4608]="*Ko ca, bhikkhave, anattā?* **";
P_HTM[4609]="*Rūpaṃ, bhikkhave, anattā; tatra vo chandarāgo pahātabbo.* **";
P_HTM[4610]="*Vedanā anattā …* **";
