P_HTM[4746]="*‘so attā so loko, so pecca bhavissāmi nicco dhuvo sassato avipariṇāmadhammo’”ti?**‘The self and the cosmos are one and the same. After passing away I will be permanent, everlasting, eternal, and imperishable’?”*";
