P_HTM[4751]="*4. Nocamesiyāsuttaṃ**It Might Not Be Mine*";
P_HTM[4752]="*Sāvatthinidānaṃ.**At Sāvatthī.*";
P_HTM[4753]="*“Kismiṃ nu kho, bhikkhave, sati, kiṃ upādāya, kiṃ abhinivissa evaṃ diṭṭhi uppajjati:**“Mendicants, when what exists, because of grasping what and insisting on what, does the view arise:*";
P_HTM[4754]="*‘no cassaṃ, no ca me siyā, nābhavissa, na me bhavissatī’”ti?**‘I might not be, and it might not be mine. I will not be, and it will not be mine’?”*";
