P_HTM[5361]="*3. Soattāsuttaṃ**This Is My Self*";
P_HTM[5362]="*Sāvatthinidānaṃ.**At Sāvatthī.*";
P_HTM[5363]="*“Kismiṃ nu kho, bhikkhave, sati, kiṃ upādāya, kiṃ abhinivissa evaṃ diṭṭhi uppajjati:**“Mendicants, when what exists, because of grasping what and insisting on what, does the view arise:*";
P_HTM[5364]="*‘so attā, so loko, so pecca bhavissāmi nicco dhuvo sassato avipariṇāmadhammo’”ti?**‘The self and the cosmos are one and the same. After passing away I will be permanent, everlasting, eternal, and imperishable’?”*";
