P_HTM[5398]="*Sāvatthinidānaṃ.**At Sāvatthī.*";
P_HTM[5399]="*“Kismiṃ nu kho, bhikkhave, sati, kiṃ upādāya, kiṃ abhinivissa evaṃ diṭṭhi uppajjati:**“Mendicants, when what exists, because of grasping what and insisting on what, does the view arise:*";
