P_HTM[5470]="*“Yampidaṃ diṭṭhaṃ sutaṃ mutaṃ viññātaṃ pattaṃ pariyesitaṃ anuvicaritaṃ manasā tampi niccaṃ vā aniccaṃ vā”ti?**“That which is seen, heard, thought, known, sought, and explored by the mind: is that permanent or impermanent?”*";
