P_HTM[6851]="*‘sāragandhe adhivatthā devā dīghāyukā vaṇṇavanto sukhabahulā’ti.**‘The gods of fairykind who live in fragrant heartwood … fragrant scents are long-lived, beautiful, and very happy.’*";
P_HTM[6852]="*Tassa evaṃ hoti:**They think:*";
P_HTM[6853]="*‘aho vatāhaṃ kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā sāragandhe adhivatthānaṃ devānaṃ … pe …**‘If only, when my body breaks up, after death, I would be reborn in the company of the gods of fairykind who live in fragrant heartwood …*";
P_HTM[6854]="*pheggugandhe adhivatthānaṃ devānaṃ …* **";
P_HTM[6855]="*tacagandhe adhivatthānaṃ devānaṃ …* **";
