P_HTM[6954]="*‘aho vatāhaṃ kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā valāhakakāyikānaṃ devānaṃ sahabyataṃ upapajjeyyan’ti.**‘If only, when my body breaks up, after death, I would be reborn in the company of the gods of the clouds!’*";
P_HTM[6955]="*So kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā valāhakakāyikānaṃ devānaṃ sahabyataṃ upapajjati.**When their body breaks up, after death, they’re reborn in the company of the gods of the clouds.*";
