P_HTM[7089]="*neva hoti na na hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇāti vā”ti?* **";
P_HTM[7090]="*“Saṅkhāresu kho, vaccha, aññāṇā, saṅkhārasamudaye aññāṇā, saṅkhāranirodhe aññāṇā, saṅkhāranirodhagāminiyā paṭipadāya aññāṇā;**“Vaccha, it is because of not knowing choices, their origin, their cessation, and the practice that leads to their cessation …”*";
P_HTM[7091]="*evamimāni anekavihitāni diṭṭhigatāni loke uppajjanti—* **";
P_HTM[7092]="*sassato lokoti vā, asassato lokoti vā … pe …* **";
