P_HTM[7115]="*“ko nu kho, bho gotama, hetu, ko paccayo, yānimāni anekavihitāni diṭṭhigatāni loke uppajjanti—**“What is the cause, Master Gotama, what is the reason why these various misconceptions arise in the world? …”*";
P_HTM[7116]="*sassato lokoti vā, asassato lokoti vā … pe …* **";
P_HTM[7117]="*neva hoti na na hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇāti vā”ti?* **";
